data.enText: a small reptile with a rough skin, four short legs and a long tail

tr: relatively long-bodied reptile with usually two pairs of legs and a tapering tail
a man who idles about in the lounges of hotels and bars in search of women who would support him

value.def: A lizard is a reptile with short legs and a long tail.

trans: (爱与时髦富人厮混的)二流子
